  ('aboriginal-f0899a01-moex-00492', 'aboriginal-f0899a01', 'aboriginal-f0899a01-moex-110-9a3b44c4', 'sub-aboriginal-f0899a01-04', NULL, 'essay', '甲因遭到乙、丙二人共同傷害而提起告訴，乙所涉之傷害罪經檢察官偵
