  ('aboriginal-f0899a01-moex-00493', 'aboriginal-f0899a01', 'aboriginal-f0899a01-moex-110-9a3b44c4', 'sub-aboriginal-f0899a01-04', NULL, 'essay', '甲因涉犯販賣毒品罪受拘提，於移送檢察官複訊時，表示欲選任律師乙
